{"word":"G1458 - ἐγκαλέω - enkaléō - eng-kal-eh'-o - Accuse","slug":"G1458","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐγκαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>enkaléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>eng-kal-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Accuse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03B3;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - egkaleo&#x0304;</b> - <i>eng-kal-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>; to <i>call in</i> (as a debt or demand), that is, <i>bring to account</i> (<i>charge</i>, <i>criminate</i>, etc.): - accuse, call in question, implead, lay to the charge."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479\">G479</a>"}]}